    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older poor-condition example best suited for someone looking for a project, parts source, or very inexpensive entry point. It shows clear age and wear throughout, with noticeable cosmetic flaws on the exterior, a tired interior, and the kind of deferred maintenance you should expect from a car in this condition. It appears complete and may be usable as-is depending on your standards, but buyers should plan on repairs, sorting, and reconditioning rather than expecting a turn-key car. Honest budget car being sold for what it is.",
