      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with solid value for someone seeking a low-cost entry point. This vehicle shows its age and will benefit from cosmetic and mechanical attention, but it offers a practical foundation for a handy owner, commuter backup, or project-minded buyer. Priced to reflect its condition while still presenting a worthwhile opportunity.",
