    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest vehicle with solid potential and a price that makes sense. Great for a first car, a daily beater, or someone handy who wants a budget-friendly project. If you want simple, usable transportation without spending a fortune, this is definitely worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Great opportunity for an enthusiast, commuter build, or weekend project. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still presents as a usable platform with a drivetrain that feels fundamentally intact and a chassis that offers solid potential. A straightforward, no-nonsense setup makes it an appealing candidate for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity and is looking for an affordable entry point. Ideal for a buyer who wants something inexpensive with room to improve, parts to refresh, and value to unlock. Priced to reflect condition while leaving plenty of upside for the next owner.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
